source:
TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The calm observer's colleague has been gone too long.
target:
TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The calm observer's colleague has been gone too long.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the Zephyros 72s to the Thalassai observer.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the Zephyros 72s to the Thalassai observer.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_000<tab>May I ask a favor? A colleague of mine from the Thalassai is overdue to make his report, and I need someone to give him a gentle nudge.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_000<tab>May I ask a favor? A colleague of mine from the Thalassai is overdue to make his report, and I need someone to give him a gentle nudge.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_001<tab>He's currently over at Rumination's Ramble, observing some life-forms newly hatched from one of our creations, but I'm afraid I'll skew the data if I show up and startle them.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_001<tab>He's currently over at Rumination's Ramble, observing some life-forms newly hatched from one of our creations, but I'm afraid I'll skew the data if I show up and startle them.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_002<tab>A familiar like you, however, should cause much less of a disruption. Would you be so kind...?
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_002<tab>A familiar like you, however, should cause much less of a disruption. Would you be so kind...?

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_003<tab>You can find my associate at Rumination's Ramble.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_003<tab>You can find my associate at Rumination's Ramble.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_004<tab>A familiar? Can I help you with something?
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_004<tab>A familiar? Can I help you with something?

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_005<tab>Oh, time to head back, is it? I was so enraptured watching the young ones frolic that I lost track of time.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_005<tab>Oh, time to head back, is it? I was so enraptured watching the young ones frolic that I lost track of time.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_006<tab>Come, come, everyone! We really must be going!
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_006<tab>Come, come, everyone! We really must be going!

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_008<tab>Still want to play, do you? I guess we shall have to appeal to your bellies, then!
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_008<tab>Still want to play, do you? I guess we shall have to appeal to your bellies, then!

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_009<tab>Would you like to try feeding them?
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_009<tab>Would you like to try feeding them?

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_010<tab>They become much more compliant after eating some of these treats. And they're so adorable when they nibble!
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_010<tab>They become much more compliant after eating some of these treats. And they're so adorable when they nibble!

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_011<tab>Go ahead and feed them some treats.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_011<tab>Go ahead and feed them some treats.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_021<tab>Isn't it fun watching them romp around?
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_021<tab>Isn't it fun watching them romp around?

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_022<tab>And they really seemed to like you! Do you work with young ones often?
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_022<tab>And they really seemed to like you! Do you work with young ones often?

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_023<tab>These babies are aquatic creatures by nature, but we're modifying them to adapt to life on land.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_023<tab>These babies are aquatic creatures by nature, but we're modifying them to adapt to life on land.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_024<tab>They mostly eat marine insects and shellfish, and some of the larger carnivores feed off them in turn.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_024<tab>They mostly eat marine insects and shellfish, and some of the larger carnivores feed off them in turn.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_025<tab>They also carry their eggs on their backs until they're ready to hatch. Fascinating, aren't they?
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_025<tab>They also carry their eggs on their backs until they're ready to hatch. Fascinating, aren't they?

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_026<tab>Oh, but that's not why you're here, is it!? I really must head back!
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_026<tab>Oh, but that's not why you're here, is it!? I really must head back!

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_028<tab>If you hadn't been sent to fetch me, I might have been out there for days.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_028<tab>If you hadn't been sent to fetch me, I might have been out there for days.

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_029<tab>In any case, it's only a matter of time before our creations are approved for release into the wild. I wonder what name they'll receive...
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERB04298_000_029<tab>In any case, it's only a matter of time before our creations are approved for release into the wild. I wonder what name they'll receive...

source: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_030<tab>Thank you for all your help today. Here, as thanks.
target: TEXT_AKTKZH003_04298_OBSERVERA04298_000_030<tab>Thank you for all your help today. Here, as thanks.
